  BUG: Verified that the vbv_delay problem HP analyzer complains is real.
       The Picture Start code is the last word of previous TP.
  Reason: picHdrPtr points to the end of a TP buffer.
          When we later point BitBuf to picHdrPtr, we forget to advance to
          the next TP!

  Check in: Fixed a bug in Reader, which caused vbv_delay probelm.


